These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, writing, singing
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Hobby   | baking | board-games | writing | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, board-games, baking, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Hobby   | board-games | magic-tricks | collecting | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, horse, cat, dog
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Pet   | rabbit | cat | horse | dog |

 #################################

 
