.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, lavender, emerald, amber
1. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
2. the person who likes lavender is between the person who likes azure and the person who likes amber##2
3. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
4. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Color   | amber | lavender | azure | emerald |

