1. the fan of rock is between the fan of gospel and the fan of jazz##2
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | rock | gospel | soul |

