2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the person driving the helicopter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2  |   3    |     4     |
| Transport   | helicopter | boat | train | jet-ski |

